      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Welcome to Red recipe run!  In this game, you will play as the little
    red riding hood, exploring in the forest.\n\nWhat tou have to do is to collect
    ingredients for the recipe given by your grandma. The ingredients can be found
    in the forest. But be careful with your time, as time passes, it will become
    nighttime. Wolves may come to attack you! Your vision will also be limited. \n\nYou
    will start from 3 health , when you are attacked, one heath point will be deducted.
    If you lose all your health, the game will be over."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dc36b3fdc14f47ebb36fd484a67e268a, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2140032, guid: dc36b3fdc14f47ebb36fd484a67e268a, type: 2}
